name: Age 18                                BALLOON IN A BOX.
description:
Balloon In A Box ( Sent Next Day )

 Choose any 18" Foil balloon for your balloon in a box !!!

 
If you want to Surprise a Male or Female friend, or a Relative on their birthday or other special occasion !!!

Sending a Balloon in a box is a fun and alternative to sending flowers and the balloon doubles up as a birthday party decoration.

 

Our Balloon In A Box Includes 

1 X 18" Foil Balloon with Tissue paper,Confetti,A Large curled Bow & Includes a Personal Message to that special person.

Please Select Man Or Lady Below.

Please enter Your message in the checkout area.

Thank you.
